            <!-- Stape DNS gotchas -->
            <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-sm">
              <p class="font-medium text-amber-800 mb-2">Common DNS pitfalls (save yourself hours):</p>
              <ul class="text-amber-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li><strong>Cloudflare users:</strong> You must <strong>disable the orange proxy cloud</strong> for your sGTM subdomain (set it to DNS-only / grey cloud). This is the #1 reason domain verification fails.</li>
                <li><strong>Duplicate records:</strong> Make sure you don't have existing A or AAAA records for the same subdomain. Remove any IPv6 (AAAA) records — they interfere with verification.</li>
                <li><strong>SSL errors:</strong> If you use Cloudflare, set SSL/TLS mode to <strong>Full</strong> for your domain. "Flexible" mode causes redirect loops.</li>
                <li><strong>Patience:</strong> DNS propagation genuinely takes time. If verification hasn't completed after 4 hours, double-check your records before changing anything.</li>
              </ul>
